function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)

--local idKnight = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "Knight")[1]
--Hydra.QActorAnim(idKnight, ANIMKEY_CRAWL)

	Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(KNIGHT_STOMP)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(KNIGHT_STOMP, STOMP_MARKER, "NPC_Walk_Fast", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(KNIGHT_STOMP, STOMP_MARKER)
	Hydra.QActorSetAnimSetOverride(KNIGHT_STOMP, KNIGHT_INSPECT_GROUND_ANIMSET)
	
end

function Start(idActorSpawned, idActorSpawner)
	
	local idKnight = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "knight_stomp")[1]
	DeathPower = Hydra.ReferencePower("death_decapitate_physical_default")
	
	Hydra.Wait(0.5)
	Hydra.QActorKill(idKnight, DeathPower)

	local tKnights = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "knight")
	for i, idActor in pairs (tKnights) do
		if Hydra.ActorIsAlive(idActor) then
			Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(idActor)
			Hydra.ActorAIForcePrimaryTarget(idActor, idActorSpawned)
			Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idActor)
			Hydra.ActorSetTeam(idActor, Hydra.TEAM_PLAYER_DEFAULT)
		end
	end

end
